If today is 02/01/1987, then one year ago from today is 1 year in the past of today, which is 02/01/1986. So the answer is 02/01/1986.

Q
Answer 02/01/1986 expected 01/02/1986
Total examples: 38 Correct answers: 11
Q: Today is 9/7. Jane is watching NFL 2003. What is the date a month ago in MM/DD/YYYY?
A:
If today is 9/7, then today is 9/7/2003. A month ago is 30 days in the past of today, which is 8/7/2003. So the answer is 8/7/2003.

