Q: Jane and John married on Jan 2, 1958. Today is their golden wedding anniversary. What is the date one year ago from today in MM/DD/YYYY?
A:
If today is their golden wedding anniversary, then today is 1/2/1958. One year ago from today is 1 year in the past of today, which is 1/2/1957. So the answer is 1/2/1957.

