Q: It was Sept. 1st, 2021 a week ago. What is the date tomorrow in MM/DD/YYYY?
A:
If it was Sept. 1st, 2021 a week ago, then it was Aug. 25th, 2021 yesterday. Today is Aug. 26th, 2021. Tomorrow is 1 day in the future of today, which is Aug. 27th, 2021. So the answer is Aug. 27th, 2021.

