Q: Yesterday was April 30, 2021. What is the date tomorrow in MM/DD/YYYY?
A:
If yesterday was April 30, 2021, then today is May 1, 2021. Tomorrow is 1 day in the future of today, which is May 2, 2021. So the answer is May 2, 2021.

